362
00:25:15,880 --> 00:25:16,720
between her and the director.

363
00:25:19,200 --> 00:25:21,720
Actually, nothing serious.

364
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:25,550
I don't know

365
00:25:25,590 --> 00:25:26,590
