366
00:25:27,350 --> 00:25:28,280
but whenever she and her mother meet,

367
00:25:28,550 --> 00:25:29,790
they argue.

368
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:31,560
And every time,

369
00:25:31,590 --> 00:25:32,430
