370
00:25:33,750 --> 00:25:35,030
Nothing I say helps.

371
00:25:35,310 --> 00:25:36,030
One says...

372
00:25:37,610 --> 00:25:38,750
"Mom doesn't understand me,"

373
00:25:39,110 --> 00:25:39,750
while the other says...

374
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,590
"This child is immature."

375
00:25:45,590 --> 00:25:46,830
Is there any...

376
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:50,440
