380
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:57,640
The two of them

381
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:59,070
just don't communicate well.

382
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,110
For example,

383
00:26:00,310 --> 00:26:01,550
