392
00:26:19,850 --> 00:26:20,640
saying in the future,

393
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:22,520
if both of us are gone,

394
00:26:22,590 --> 00:26:23,690
leaving Chun alone,

395
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,790
what will happen to her?

396
00:26:26,530 --> 00:26:27,630
I say, why don't you express these concerns

397
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:30,270
properly to Chun?

398
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,180
But she won't.

399
00:26:32,750 --> 00:26:33,890
As for Chun,

400
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:35,880
young people have their own ideas.

401
00:26:37,310 --> 00:26:38,470
I respect that.

402
00:26:39,070 --> 00:26:39,870
But she

403
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:40,870
doesn't say anything

404
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,240
to her mother either.

405
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:43,770
It's understandable.

406
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:46,500
Her mom is quick-tempered.

407
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:47,480
When they start talking,

408
00:26:47,550 --> 00:26:48,680
they often end up in an argument.

409
00:26:50,000 --> 00:26:50,680
I don't know

410
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:52,000
when

411
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:53,400
they started

412
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,480
being like this.

413
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:57,680
I remember when she was little,

414
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,320
she and her mother

415
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:01,350
got along very well together.

416
00:27:02,350 --> 00:27:03,750
Once, on Chun's birthday,

417
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:04,750
her mother...

418
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:07,550
Oh, right.

419
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:09,200
There's a video.

420
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:12,880
What video?

421
00:27:41,890 --> 00:27:43,580
[Xu Tongsheng]

422
00:27:42,560 --> 00:27:43,430
We'll be there right away.

423
00:27:55,750 --> 00:27:56,750
Tongsheng, you're here!

424
00:27:56,830 --> 00:27:57,820
You're back, Director.

425
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:58,640
Sit back down.

426
00:27:59,220 --> 00:28:00,590
It's so good to have you here.

427
00:28:00,610 --> 00:28:01,150
Here.

428
00:28:01,210 --> 00:28:02,480
Let me pour you some water. Have you had anything to drink?

429
00:28:02,550 --> 00:28:03,420
I'll do it myself! I'll do it myself!

430
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:04,750
Let me, let me. You sit.

431
00:28:08,310 --> 00:28:08,680
Here.

432
00:28:08,810 --> 00:28:09,800
Okay, thank you.

433
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:11,640
