434
00:28:13,070 --> 00:28:14,440
I came today mainly...

435
00:28:14,750 --> 00:28:16,600
to talk to you

436
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,070
about Jin Chun.

437
00:28:21,360 --> 00:28:22,910
I can't control her anymore.

438
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:24,640
I don't plan to interfere anymore.

439
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:27,720
She can do whatever she wants.

440
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:32,030
Director,

441
00:28:32,590 --> 00:28:34,290
don't you feel that the issues...

442
00:28:34,590 --> 00:28:36,090
between you and Jin Chun...

443
00:28:37,110 --> 00:28:38,200
are getting more serious?

444
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:39,590
Yes,

445
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:41,310
there are issues.

446
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:42,790
But I don't know

447
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:43,830
where the issues lie.

448
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:45,880
Whenever we talk

449
00:28:45,960 --> 00:28:46,830
or meet,

450
00:28:47,350 --> 00:28:48,480
regardless of the reason,

451
00:28:48,750 --> 00:28:49,750
we always part on bad terms.

452
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:52,240
She says I meddle in her affairs,

453
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,680
but she also interferes in mine

454
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:57,440
without my permission.

455
00:28:58,240 --> 00:28:59,150
She went behind my back,

456
00:28:59,550 --> 00:29:00,650
contacted the Civil Affairs Bureau

457
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:01,890
and other welfare houses,

458
00:29:02,070 --> 00:29:03,930
and forcibly took away

459
00:29:04,000 --> 00:29:05,770
a sick child of mine.

460
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,720
Tongsheng, you know it.

461
00:29:07,970 --> 00:29:09,820
Every child in this institution

462
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:11,550
is like my own flesh and blood.

463
00:29:11,590 --> 00:29:12,880
How could I bear to part with them?

464
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:14,590
Yes.

465
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,560
How could she do that to me?

466
00:29:16,750 --> 00:29:18,450
Yes, I... I understand.

467
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:19,270
I understand everything

468
00:29:19,310 --> 00:29:20,400
