472
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:27,680
the whole picture?

473
00:29:34,030 --> 00:29:35,200
Let me show you something.

474
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:38,590
Look.

475
00:29:40,880 --> 00:29:41,880
It's Yu.

476
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:42,490
Yes.

477
00:29:43,110 --> 00:29:44,160
This was recorded after Yu was transferred to

478
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,810
