479
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:47,100
She recovered really fast,

480
00:29:47,310 --> 00:29:48,300
didn't she?

481
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:50,160
She's even smiling.

482
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,590
She's doing so much better than before.

483
00:29:55,030 --> 00:29:56,760
Jin Chun also grew up in the welfare house.

484
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:58,290
She thinks just like you do.

485
00:29:58,400 --> 00:29:59,990
She wants what's best for the kids too.

486
00:30:01,120 --> 00:30:02,240
Remember the presentation

487
00:30:02,270 --> 00:30:03,120
