493
00:30:12,850 --> 00:30:13,890
That's why I didn't tell you.

494
00:30:16,550 --> 00:30:17,270
Really?

495
00:30:17,510 --> 00:30:18,160
Really.

496
00:30:19,810 --> 00:30:21,300
Well, that was a good thing.

497
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:22,680
Why didn't she tell me?

498
00:30:25,870 --> 00:30:26,590
Director,

499
00:30:27,260 --> 00:30:28,970
