503
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:36,510
But to be honest,

504
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:38,750
for Chun,

505
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:40,480
you are indeed...

506
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:43,310
much better to us than to her.

507
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,000
It's not comparable.

508
00:30:48,270 --> 00:30:49,680
Unlike you,

509
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:52,070
she has parents.

510
00:30:53,790 --> 00:30:55,680
She must be much happier than you are.

511
00:30:56,830 --> 00:30:57,640
Tongsheng.

512
00:30:58,750 --> 00:31:00,890
The attention I give to all of you

513
00:31:01,160 --> 00:31:02,790
