514
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:06,480
Is it possible

515
00:31:07,290 --> 00:31:08,780
that this kind of thinking...

516
00:31:09,890 --> 00:31:11,390
is exactly what's making the distance...

517
00:31:11,540 --> 00:31:13,060
between you and Chun grow larger?

518
00:31:14,390 --> 00:31:15,240
That's why she's stopped

519
00:31:15,240 --> 00:31:16,400
saying anything to you?

520
00:31:21,770 --> 00:31:23,540
After all these years, she's gotten used to being...

521
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:26,110
independent, strong, and mature.

522
00:31:27,270 --> 00:31:28,280
When she encounters problems,

523
00:31:28,790 --> 00:31:30,240
she just silently endures them alone,

524
00:31:30,600 --> 00:31:31,510
not telling anyone.

525
00:31:34,480 --> 00:31:35,440
Recently...

526
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:38,850
